{"tid":1847153,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"講真 比著係您會點做？","createTime":"2020-01-28T02:49:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T03:35:44.000Z","uid":190334,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8195f92f966f7be8e6a64130efd7e1edad078d99","tid":1847153,"uid":190334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T02:49:36.000Z","msg":"事咁的 <br />\n另一半因為探親而番大陸(東莞<br />\n然後我都有叫佢唔好番<br />\n佢又話：唉咁無計啦 一年一次<br />\n然後佢番左黎香港<br />\n我娘親又係咁叫我唔好去接觸佢<br />\n話：唔好見面啦 有潛伏期呀 隔多幾日先見啦<br />\n<br />\n我心諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大佬 我前日先約左人 而家又要我咁推人<br />\n其實唔見佢 又好似好安全，但係顯得我好自私囉<br />\n<br />\n加上而家女朋友又嬲鳩左我咁<br />\n有時夾左喺佢哋兩個中間真係好攰囉<br />\n<br />\n尤其係做啲決策嘅時候呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係頭都痛撚埋架<br />\n<br />\n又要成日都去諗另一邊感受果種feel <br />\n以前女朋友成日話我唔識顧佢感受<br />\nok 我進步 我改善 我嘗試呀<br />\n但手心手背都係肉，成日都要我揀<br />\n<br />\n比著係您會點做？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JWCjGmg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJWCjGmg.jpg&h=4c2bd0af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9HwXs1k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9HwXs1k.jpg&h=8caa4f17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"567bc3caafff5979feb18e01cfd0b4a2b057bdd2","tid":1847153,"uid":3356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T02:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee891df3ab8abfc25e41b33cc4f7fc513a8fe83","tid":1847153,"uid":189138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T02:51:35.000Z","msg":"中出即飛"},{"pid":"d36733291303be81f7c63d34da862bc8ba129211","tid":1847153,"uid":201414,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T02:53:19.000Z","msg":"呢啲女飛得"},{"pid":"89e22fef55972c12f752cd8e1d5c7a19945b794f","tid":1847153,"uid":71166,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"repl